{"tid":1517507,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［屌你咁撚CUTE］樹熊拍廣告獲價值五萬片酬 　望有效提升環境保護關注度","createTime":"2019-08-30T02:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T08:30:10.000Z","uid":109136,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e448a77f4159d9ce55fe5c4901728f5f755d425a","tid":1517507,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:53:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_grpNHlhX5A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_grpNHlhX5A&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8kXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=513c7878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_grpNHlhX5A</a><br />\n<br />\n這隻18個月大的樹熊接受了1.2萬棵桉樹的報酬，這些桉樹將被種植在新省和昆省的樹熊棲息地。Arlo的飼養員，來自Wildlife HQ Zoo的Jarrod Schenk表示，Arol天生具有鏡頭感。即使周圍都是工作人員，牠也表現得非常放鬆、冷靜和有耐心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/australia/2019/08/20190826_au_koala.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Faustralia%2F2019%2F08%2F20190826_au_koala.jpg&h=e2007553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSchenk補充指，Arol坐在拖車裡的一個洗衣籃裡的畫面看似很簡單，但其實沒有多少樹熊能呆坐在那裡那麼久，然而這對Arlo來說卻很容易，非常出眾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/australia/2019/08/20190826_au_koala1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Faustralia%2F2019%2F08%2F20190826_au_koala1.jpg&h=88346761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nArlo和其兄弟姐妹Jemima和Mango也參加了旨在保護樹熊桉樹家園的最新NRMA保險活動。這5萬澳元將捐給澳洲環保志願者組織，該組織致力於在澳洲各地積極恢復和維護樹熊的棲息地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/australia/2019/08/20190826_au_koala2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Faustralia%2F2019%2F08%2F20190826_au_koala2.jpg&h=06bb6082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於樹熊每天需要20個小時的睡眠，攝製隊不得不充分利用有限的拍攝時間。Schenk表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">Arlo每拍15分鐘便要睡覺，所以他們花了四天時間才完成拍攝。他又透露，片場到處都放著大束新鮮的桉樹葉子，好讓樹熊們能繼續工作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/australia/2019/08/20190826_au_koala3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Faustralia%2F2019%2F08%2F20190826_au_koala3.jpg&h=ca11601c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他希望在廣告播出後Arlo能引起人們的注意。他表示，他們將繼續接受環保工作預約，樹熊正面臨絕種，這則廣告將有助於提高人們對該問題的認識和關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4975508?variant=zh-tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F4975508%3Fvariant%3Dzh-tw&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8kXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=9cfde90b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4975508?variant=zh-tw</a>"},{"pid":"c5774f7640607061a1fe1bccfb8dc022bc235c82","tid":1517507,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8kXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=88c501e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8kXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=e1c5544a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8kXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=16c5b98f\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"bd904062b6a9bdfc11a71f57ead6dcd088085e8f","tid":1517507,"uid":282166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:29:49.000Z","msg":"好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ff11ff26d55e7b4a937842680109892c2a8e6d","tid":1517507,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd904062b6a9bdfc11a71f57ead6dcd088085e8f","tid":1517507,"uid":282166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:29:49.000Z","msg":"好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:30:10.000Z","msg":"世界第一可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}